These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: papayaade, sprite
There 2 different types of food: cherry, papaya
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking papayaade##3
2. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | sprite  | papayaade |
| Food       | cherry | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | 7up | lemonade |
| Sport      | snowboarding     | tennis  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
There are 2 different nationalities: american, brazilian
1. the american is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the american is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | martial-arts  |
| Nationality   | american | brazilian |

 #################################

 
