.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig
1. the pakistani is on the left or right of the british##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | british | pakistani |
| Pet           | guinea-pig     | chinchilla  |

