.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, dancer
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | cooking |
| Job     | engineer        | dancer |

